вҹҰ TEST: mkdir can be typed using a named record type вҹ§

вҹҰ Define the options type (must come before extern that references it) вҹ§
t MkdirOptions = { recursive: рқ”№ }

вҹҰ Typed extern with record type parameter вҹ§
e fsвӢ…promises : {
  mkdir : О»(рқ•Ҡ, MkdirOptions) вҶ’ рқ•Ң
}

вҹҰ Create typed options вҹ§
c opts=({recursive:вҠӨ}:MkdirOptions)

вҹҰ Now this typechecks! вҹ§
О»ensureDir(dir:рқ•Ҡ)вҶ’рқ•Ң=
  fsвӢ…promises.mkdir(dir, opts)

О»main()вҶ’рқ•Ң=()
